      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW229345005 BCX0">When Faiza Banu discovered that the Silver Mountain School of Hotel Management in her hometown of Kathmandu in Nepal provided a prestigious hospitality course with a degree from Queen Margaret University, she knew she was on the path to success. </span></p>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW229345005 BCX0">Graduating in 2023, with a <a href="/about-the-university/quality/programme-specifications/ba-international-hospitality-tourism-and-events-management-silver-mountain/">BA International Hospitality and Tourism Management</a>, along with a prize for being top of her class, Faiza tells us about her experience on the course, and how it has led to an exhilarating job opportunity following graduation.</span> </p>]]></Value>
